Package: unigent
Architecture: all
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3 (>= 3.10), python3-requests, python3-dotenv
Description: UniGent Autonomous AI Agent
 A universal autonomous AI agent powered by NVIDIA NIM API.
 It features streaming responses, persistent memory, file operations, shell commands, web search, parallel tool execution, and more.
 This package is architecture-independent (Python).
 Note: The 'openai' Python package is required but not available from Debian/Ubuntu. Install it manually:
   pip3 install openai
 Or use the package from PyPI: python3 -m pip install openai